snippet.title: Henry Cavill does NOT believe Amber Heard!?
snippet.description:
Amber Heard has been the center of attention for a while now. After the audio recordings of her ADMITTING to abusing Johnny Depp and MOCKING him, it's hard to believe that she could possibly ever be deemed "innocent." The recordings clearly indicate in my opinion that Amber Heard is a lying abuser, which makes you wonder, who else is aware of this? 
Cavill has been centered around controversy as well, as a result of social media attempting to shut him down over his opinions, regarding the MeToo movement. I am very curious what he thinks about this situation.
